{"tid":1869631,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"網友票選 K Pop 最美歌手排行榜出爐！子瑜、太妍、允兒通通輸給她！","createTime":"2020-02-08T09:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T03:16:04.000Z","uid":34489,"like":10,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"21fb5e10947ff838ebca44480f0d8ffa39da885f","tid":1869631,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T09:35:54.000Z","msg":"每年年末都會有很多網絡的票選舉行，例如網民最愛的韓劇、最喜歡的藝人等，在剛剛過去的 2019 年，南韓的網民亦有在芸芸貌美的 K Pop 女歌手中，投票選出了 100 位他們認為最美的歌手。一些我們熟悉的臉孔都通通上榜，例如少女時代的允兒、太妍、Twice 的子瑜、以及近日被爆出戀情的大勢偶像 Blackpink 的 Jennie 等。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>第 10 位 － Mina@Twice<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/O7vftcY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FO7vftcY.png&h=298e47e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 9 位 － Nana@After Scool<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jkMgUbL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjkMgUbL.png&h=d4f3d1f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 8 位 － Jennie@Blackpink<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XwXsKmq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXwXsKmq.png&h=c2745b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 7 位 － Taeyeon@Girls&rsquo; Generation<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wtMJ6cR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwtMJ6cR.png&h=9f5ea4d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 6 位 － Krystal@f(x)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DwBvywT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDwBvywT.png&h=fd35a90d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 5 位 － Jisoo@Blackpink<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bxg5CM5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fbxg5CM5.png&h=f85464c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 4 位 － Tzuyu@Twice<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RsKnKgE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRsKnKgE.png&h=5ab78a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 3 位 － Yoona@Girls&rsquo; Generation<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Pom7QtM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPom7QtM.png&h=17bfb88a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第 2 位 － Irene@Red Velvet<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/zB4th8W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzB4th8W.png&h=53fd5a33&s={SIZE}\" /></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n而冠軍寶座就由 WJSN 的 Luda 奪得！其實也不難理解吧，她一向都是團中的「門面擔當」，而且早前她才成為了韓國女生門的整容範本，韓國網民認為她漂亮也是很合理的！<br />\n<strong><ins>第 1 位 － Luda@WJSN</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/FlashyTediousAtlanticridleyturtle-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FFlashyTediousAtlanticridleyturtle-size_restricted.gif&h=46df1be8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8e0061db5d472efd52d6205689992f282a96ba9","tid":1869631,"uid":205928,"like":15,"dislike":14,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T09:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ygzzwG3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FygzzwG3.jpg&h=15d3e388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nluda QQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f00bb5ccc7d1b2b7fb5518947513764fd484fe0","tid":1869631,"uid":220236,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T09:37:38.000Z","msg":"Jisoo先第五？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dcf3cd777e3e43e9ec73588d6c6f4349ff424ad","tid":1869631,"uid":555,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T09:37:43.000Z","msg":"mina泰妍不啦"},{"pid":"618e618c15115041eb813baee109eefecf284140","tid":1869631,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f8e0061db5d472efd52d6205689992f282a96ba9","tid":1869631,"uid":205928,"like":15,"dislike":14,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T09:37:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https: